16 WHEREAS, Marjy is also an accomplished author, having written Real Estate Asset
17 Management: Executive Strategies for Profit Making and Blighted, a compelling narrative
18 on the two-year redevelopment of the Summerdale apartment community; and
19 WHEREAS, her unwavering dedication to building community trust and improving lives
20 extends beyond housing as she continues to lead with vision and integrity in her mission to
21 create safe, healthy, and equitable living environments for underserved populations; and
22 WHEREAS, it is abundantly fitting and proper that this remarkable individual be
23 appropriately honored during this special time.
24 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
25 the members of this body commend Margaret "Marjy" Stagmeier for her exceptional
26 contributions to affordable housing, equitable community development, and educational
27 support for families as well as extend best wishes for continued success.
28 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
29 and directed to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to
30 Margaret "Marjy" Stagmeier.
